Editable prompts/skills — Stage C: dashboard Authoring panel (viewer + editor)

Completes the in-dashboard prompts/skills editor (item: "markdown viewer →
editor"). Built on the modular dashboard/src/.

- dashboard/src/panels/authoring.js + an "Authoring" sidebar panel:
  - browse prompts (soul/*.md) and skills (grouped by category, source-badged
    builtin/workspace);
  - markdown Preview (via `marked`) + raw Edit toggle;
  - Save (PUT -> live reload), Reload-from-disk (POST /api/authoring/reload),
    Delete (workspace skills only), and "Save as new" / "+ New Skill" (clone a
    built-in as a template, prefilled with a SKILL.md scaffold).
- index.html: nav item + empty panel-authoring container (JS-rendered).
- main.js: import + panelTitles + switchPanel dispatch.
- marked added as a devDependency (bundled into dist by esbuild; ~68 KB).

Verified: dashboard build clean (loadAuthoring + marked bundled, token
placeholder + the 3 window.* globals intact); npm test green (34 unit + API +
smoke). Acceptance gate: Mercury visual click-through.

